超過"},{"pid":"105f811f7abdcd116061f4c6a82d43d0580fcdd3","tid":2446654,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:45:06.000Z","msg":"有冇記者朋友今日去金錢村欣賞壁畫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f418dc6653d76af06ef217664b62dbf0645133","tid":2446654,"uid":382921,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:53:51.000Z","msg":"叫你去佢屋企畫畫<br />\n剩低個班幼教都肯？<br />\n咁唔合理都肯奶<br />\n教師喎，春風化雨喎，以生命影響生命喎"},{"pid":"906d2d65e31df8cbc0e956212c6b533342a299b2","tid":2446654,"uid":121029,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"a6f418dc6653d76af06ef217664b62dbf0645133","tid":2446654,"uid":382921,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:53:51.000Z","msg":"叫你去佢屋企畫畫<br />\n剩低個班幼教都肯？<br />\n咁唔合理都肯奶<br />\n教師喎，春風化雨喎，以生命影響生命喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"Please 睇多次內文同記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老師有反抗 有唔同意，結果換嚟校長同主任修改教職員簽左名嘅會議記錄（由反對改為同意）<br />\n事後，老師要報警要求警方做證人校長先拎返本修改左嘅會議記錄。<br />\n<br />\n同時，有老師向edb投訴呢件事，結果換嚟edb 向校長篤灰邊個姓嘅老師投訴，仲同各位老師講投訴係冇用<br />\n<br />\n各位老師要做嘅都做左，<br />\n你地要記著 離職係個人選擇，但新入職嘅老師都會有同樣遭遇。係離唔離職嘅問題定間學校有問題？"},{"pid":"c030ac51fd4844f289cf9d231eb6e62e66fb075f","tid":2446654,"uid":149559,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"啲幼師又好好咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼打鬼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c8edaa6749df367669c78b5db3743dee442629","tid":2446654,"uid":155377,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699d9faa24a1ee4d78bf1bb74816d2962bb85dde","tid":2446654,"uid":382841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"修改會議紀錄<br />\n算唔算不誠實使用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b0403ef3c473f2dbc37ad320f3d5a30566ccfb","tid":2446654,"uid":365791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"好奸個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5619b170ec478c7eddccf1cbfd189ebf07604b76","tid":2446654,"uid":155377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"699d9faa24a1ee4d78bf1bb74816d2962bb85dde","tid":2446654,"uid":382841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"修改會議紀錄<br />\n算唔算不誠實使用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"虛假文書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93239f8fe8145af48f93b5cd3fd4f9f616dbfe4b","tid":2446654,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:54:45.000Z","msg":"校長屋企整壁畫 係接近老細叫個秘書去佢屋企拎D衫去乾洗, 順便喂埋隻狗, 清埋D狗屎......<br />\n<br />\n做得咁多間學校校長, 連賓賓都請唔起..?!<br />\n縮數度到盡?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52687266a81f64571b0dbdc275d0ebadffcf693c","tid":2446654,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:26:56.000Z","msg":"又係賤女人做校長，估撚到你啦"},{"pid":"a842e8a2a6dd5b372f26d4fe7781a717e7767b21","tid":2446654,"uid":57644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d27665582121b184ffa19d302270ab5d9642094","tid":2446654,"uid":269202,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:18:44.000Z","msg":"聽聞幼稚園好多額外job, 例如專題教學： 交通月、生日、畢業典禮等，要用星期六、日同放學後去趕進度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但去校長屋企整壁畫就太超過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:11:52.000Z","msg":"根本就係公器私用"},{"pid":"1dea828fbb16be3b428463bb158aa142799ebcf7","tid":2446654,"uid":264324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5619b170ec478c7eddccf1cbfd189ebf07604b76","tid":2446654,"uid":155377,"like":1,"dislike":0,